Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.42,0:00:11.27,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}On the way back from getting chocolate for Valentine's,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.27,0:00:13.37,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I bought lipstick as well.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.36,0:00:19.04,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I know this colour doesn't suit me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.98,0:00:22.40,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I know this, but...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.40,0:00:24.82,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have to do this.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.85,0:00:34.82,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be5\blur5\org(0,0)\fad(2000,0)}Shoujo Sect
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.85,0:00:34.82,Title_alt,,0000,0000,0000,,{\org(0,0)\be5\blur5\fad(2000,0)}Shoujo Sect
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.55,0:00:34.82,Title No. 2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(3000,0)}3rd Period
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.27,0:00:43.80,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Maya! We're going to leave without you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.33,0:00:45.92,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.27,0:00:50.84,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for taking so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.08,0:00:53.60,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Really, how long were you planning on keeping us...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.11,0:00:56.37,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for making you wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.53,0:01:02.38,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Shinobu, is there something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.34,0:01:05.88,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Kirin. You can go on ahead to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.63,0:01:10.18,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Maya, come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.18,0:01:12.08,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to the reflection room together.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.49,0:01:13.39,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.24,0:01:16.69,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell the school that we'll be late.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.72,0:01:35.36,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,It's cold, isn't it? Do you feel the chill?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.99,0:01:37.11,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.07,0:01:40.08,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first time I've used this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.51,0:01:42.84,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean the reflection room?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.13,0:01:46.94,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,If you commit an infraction, you're to stay locked up in here for a whole night.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.84,0:01:49.06,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.45,0:01:52.59,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are we here?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.84,0:01:53.91,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.53,0:01:57.73,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, kiss me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.48,0:02:10.23,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I can taste your jealousy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.32,0:02:12.11,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm not...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.53,0:02:20.66,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Amants en Nécessité nombre cinquante.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.66,0:02:22.47,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,The one Naito uses.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.23,0:02:26.40,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my fault...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.40,0:02:27.98,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,...to make you feel this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.64,0:02:31.68,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,But I like you just as you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.22,0:02:34.20,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,You're mistaken! It's just a coincidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.34,0:02:37.68,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.64,0:02:46.46,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Maya. Come to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.29,0:03:01.89,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.13,0:03:03.46,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.76,0:03:08.11,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't Handa and Miss Maya with you today?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.81,0:03:10.33,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Mumps...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.33,0:03:11.62,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.08,0:03:14.49,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,...is what I'm sure they don't have.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.49,0:03:17.26,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just call it the curse of Valentine's.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.22,0:04:18.33,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I touch you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.64,0:04:22.87,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Wherever you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.90,0:04:26.45,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.45,0:04:29.13,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Maya, can you position your behind here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.20,0:04:31.97,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Do as I say.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.69,0:04:34.55,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.33,0:04:36.78,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,E-Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.90,0:04:40.02,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,That's good. Stop there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.96,0:04:58.50,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Do me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.93,0:05:00.27,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.42,0:05:17.02,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you use Naito's lipstick?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.03,0:05:20.18,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a coincidence, like I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.68,0:05:22.95,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder... Is that the truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.00,0:05:30.18,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Shinobu!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.18,0:05:33.63,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't be leaving here if you continue to lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.43,0:05:50.13,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.13,0:05:52.99,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw it yesterday in a store.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.46,0:05:54.85,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,And I thought of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.25,0:06:01.60,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I was buying lots of chocolates.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.60,0:06:02.88,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.88,0:06:05.08,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,One of my favourite chocolates as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.65,0:06:06.76,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.89,0:06:12.72,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I should have known better...\Nbut I wanted to be closer to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.28,0:06:16.04,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted you to look at me more.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.43,0:06:17.75,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.06,0:06:29.19,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,You're always gentle when you do it.
