Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.59,0:07:02.17,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.74,0:07:06.10,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, were you busy this morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.27,0:07:07.81,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,You could say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.64,0:07:12.62,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to eat all of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.62,0:07:14.21,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, of course I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.02,0:07:17.70,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing. I'm kind of impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.70,0:07:20.37,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you're making me feel bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.81,0:07:23.52,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,You can have just one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.50,0:07:27.27,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait a...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.89,0:07:29.32,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.37,0:07:34.03,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Here. This is for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.96,0:07:36.64,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.64,0:07:38.88,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,It's chocolates of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.55,0:07:40.73,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,For me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.16,0:07:43.57,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,It is Valentine's Day, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.21,0:07:45.47,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.28,0:07:47.86,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.20,0:07:52.57,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Les Fleurs Du Chocolat!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.57,0:07:54.60,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I always wanted to try these!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.60,0:07:56.58,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a nice person, Handa.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.73,0:08:07.81,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if she even savours what she's eating.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.81,0:08:11.59,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Naito is like that because she's sensitive to taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.97,0:08:14.16,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised you know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.51,0:08:19.00,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, she's the one who Lady Shinobu likes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.74,0:08:25.70,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt she's that happy just because of those chocolates.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.46,0:08:28.53,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.53,0:08:31.74,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Shinobu doesn't look like she's being rewarded for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.35,0:08:34.65,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's better that way, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.65,0:08:35.74,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,For you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.82,0:09:04.88,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Handa...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.01,0:09:12.08,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,For you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.08,0:09:13.46,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.06,0:09:15.72,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,That's for answering for me at roll call.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.49,0:09:26.17,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Naito.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.17,0:09:27.84,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.76,0:09:32.17,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that about?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.58,0:09:36.06,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's with that attitude?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.41,0:09:39.06,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,It's rude to be angry all of a sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.38,0:09:41.80,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,What did I do to you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.97,0:09:43.93,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't play dumb!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.26,0:09:45.25,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.25,0:09:46.45,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,About the chocolates!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.45,0:09:48.53,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,You gave her some didn't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.81,0:09:51.20,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,That was out of courtesy. Courtesy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.57,0:09:54.18,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,You just give chocolate to everyone, don't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.18,0:09:55.83,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,While making them think otherwise!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.83,0:09:59.13,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you assume you know what I feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.13,0:10:00.46,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not so virtuous either!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.46,0:10:03.01,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that? What did I do to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.34,0:10:05.35,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Lots of things!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.35,0:10:09.26,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,You went out with a teacher right after I confessed to you, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.33,0:10:10.49,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,That was...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.03,0:10:13.33,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Usually, it's the one who was rejected who gets to be angry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.33,0:10:18.00,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you spew what you hear from rumors at me and still expect an apology!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.10,0:10:20.89,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you know how I felt back then?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.40,0:10:24.66,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,So you should know how I feel right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.91,0:10:29.20,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.39,0:10:33.84,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the idiot...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.68,0:10:37.16,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Why was Miss Naito angry?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.16,0:10:38.74,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,She's jealous, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.74,0:10:41.63,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it more like a lovers' quarrel?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.35,0:10:46.44,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ogami? Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.70,0:10:53.33,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey attic girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.33,0:10:55.12,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,The bath is free now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.60,0:10:56.86,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.60,0:10:59.24,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,You can go first.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.24,0:11:01.40,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll come as soon as I finish cleaning up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.86,0:11:38.32,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for calling you all the way out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.03,0:11:41.32,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,What was it you wanted to talk about?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.72,0:11:45.27,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm having my birthday party in my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.27,0:11:46.68,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you come, Miss Handa?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.68,0:11:48.45,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,You have my congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.85,0:11:51.24,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,However, I'm going to be quite busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.24,0:11:52.10,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.67,0:11:56.11,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't given you a date yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.11,0:11:59.56,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be very busy for a long while, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.56,0:12:01.02,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.02,0:12:02.53,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Please excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.53,0:12:03.94,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got some guts to do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.56,0:12:09.73,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you mention it, this reminds me of a rumor I've heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.48,0:12:14.50,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, some girls went to an upperclassman's birthday party they were invited to...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.50,0:12:17.62,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,...but upon arriving, found themselves to be the only ones there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.62,0:12:22.13,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, they weren't allowed to go home until she was done with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.64,0:12:27.18,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Conveniently, that upperclassman seemed to have a birthday party every month.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.59,0:12:29.94,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you implying that I am that same person?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.94,0:12:31.30,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.30,0:12:33.20,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a rumour.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.20,0:12:35.53,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like the Phantom Doll Legend. {I know it's a mistranslation but leave "phantom doll" so that it will not conflict with episode 1}
