Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.21,0:12:49.71,Signs - Text,,0000,0030,0320,,{\fs30\pos(320,70)}Art Room
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.15,0:12:56.42,Signs,,0000,0030,0320,,{\fad(0,0)}{\pos(320,75)}{\p1}{\bord0.5\shad0}m 0 0 l 200 0 200 50 0 50{\p0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.15,0:12:56.42,Signs - Text,,0000,0030,0320,,{\fs30\pos(320,70)}Sorry about yesterday
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.04,0:12:59.82,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Handa?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.28,0:13:01.18,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.77,0:13:04.19,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Naito was looking for you just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.44,0:13:08.42,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,She said she's waiting for you in the Math prep room.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.37,0:13:11.60,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,But isn't she on lock up duty?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.86,0:13:14.28,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems another girl is doing it today.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.28,0:13:15.70,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.05,0:13:17.70,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll go see if she's there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.20,0:13:22.20,Signs,,0000,0030,0320,,{\fad(0,0)}{\pos(320,75)}{\p1}{\bord0.5\shad0}m 0 0 l 260 0 260 50 0 50{\p0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.20,0:13:22.20,Signs - Text,,0000,0030,0320,,{\fs30\pos(320,70)}Mini Café - Blue Giver
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.99,0:13:30.14,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Shinobu said it's okay for us to go back first, but what will you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.54,0:13:33.21,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Should we wait a bit longer?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.93,0:13:35.49,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe we should.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.49,0:13:38.48,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I do feel like being less of a sloth at the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.04,0:13:42.69,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Although, no matter how this is resolved, my feelings will stay the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.63,0:13:46.87,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,You just won't give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.20,0:13:49.84,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you the same, Kirin?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.02,0:13:50.93,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.58,0:13:53.50,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a bit more complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.05,0:13:58.93,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Although I don't think I'll ever stop being Lady Shinobu's maid.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.50,0:14:03.00,Signs,,0000,0030,0320,,{\fad(0,0)}{\pos(320,75)}{\p1}{\bord0.5\shad0}m 0 0 l 260 0 260 50 0 50{\p0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.50,0:14:03.00,Signs - Text,,0000,0030,0320,,{\fs30\pos(320,70)}Mathematics Preparation Room
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.14,0:14:06.77,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is Miss Naito?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.05,0:14:11.54,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome to my birthday party.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.93,0:14:36.10,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,She was seen entering a hotel wearing our uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.63,0:14:39.46,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone I know sent that to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.46,0:14:43.10,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,She'd be expelled if the school ever found out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.65,0:14:46.13,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.13,0:14:47.58,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Do I really need to tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.99,0:14:50.61,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Promise me you won't lay a hand on Naito!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.07,0:14:53.61,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll just have to listen to what I say, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.84,0:15:02.66,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.66,0:15:04.33,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm locking up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.44,0:15:16.71,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Handa?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.00,0:15:35.11,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,You really are beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.11,0:15:38.15,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,But you know, just looking isn't enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.91,0:15:55.89,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.15,0:16:04.67,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Take me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.23,0:16:10.47,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't do as I say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.44,0:16:16.22,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Wai...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.22,0:16:18.41,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, I want you inside me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.93,0:16:31.52,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! That's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.52,0:16:32.92,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Deeper!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.00,0:16:35.79,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.57,0:16:59.33,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.33,0:17:00.59,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.59,0:17:02.49,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't that embarrassing is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.41,0:17:06.28,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.14,0:17:10.95,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,We've been interrupted.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.95,0:17:14.24,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's continue this next time, okay, Miss Handa?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.92,0:17:18.11,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.77,0:17:35.83,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.55,0:17:41.65,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,The message in the arts room.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.65,0:17:43.15,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,That was you, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.32,0:17:47.56,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.56,0:17:49.15,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,You're always like this, Miss Handa.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.96,0:17:53.92,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.06,0:18:21.61,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,The school was thrown into chaos after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.06,0:18:25.55,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Ogami entered university.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.99,0:18:28.44,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Naito is transferring schools.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.11,0:18:35.15,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,As for Lady Shinobu, she has barely left the reflection room since.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.65,0:18:35.15,Signs,,0000,0030,0320,,{\fad(0,0)}{\pos(320,75)}{\p1}{\bord0.5\shad0}m 0 0 l 200 0 200 50 0 50{\p0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.65,0:18:35.15,Signs - Text,,0000,0030,0320,,{\fs30\pos(320,70)}Reflection Room
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.00,0:18:37.55,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Shinobu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.01,0:18:41.89,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Shinobu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.08,0:18:56.59,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Shinobu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.59,0:18:58.49,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't find her anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.69,0:18:59.57,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.80,0:19:12.32,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.69,0:19:14.94,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Shinobu's disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.53,0:19:20.13,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,She feels responsible for what's happened to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.13,0:19:21.82,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,She's so sensitive.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.32,0:19:24.47,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,You think I know where she is?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.47,0:19:27.55,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's not like I knew her for very long.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.13,0:19:30.75,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I think you two would have a better idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.36,0:19:32.51,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't screw with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.51,0:19:35.84,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,You and Lady Shinobu met when you were children!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.52,0:19:39.01,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,You played hide-and-seek in a park, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.01,0:19:40.70,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.70,0:19:44.36,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,You kissed her when she left the park.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.36,0:19:45.61,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.37,0:19:47.35,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Kirin...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.35,0:19:49.61,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it. We'll just look for her ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.02,0:19:52.37,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,In a park?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.16,0:19:55.39,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,We kissed?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.53,0:20:05.67,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.46,0:20:17.06,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.06,0:20:19.20,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.53,0:20:26.78,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.40,0:20:29.59,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.88,0:20:35.12,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Handa.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.97,0:20:38.19,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Naito.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.73,0:20:41.33,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Found you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.95,0:20:47.99,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I'm late.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.38,0:20:52.18,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,You're very late.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.18,0:20:53.15,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Dummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.97,0:20:57.86,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, she was freezing...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.86,0:20:59.81,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,so I thought I'd take her somewhere warm first.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.22,0:21:01.94,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll see her home after she's calmed down.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.93,0:21:04.22,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.50,0:21:47.61,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Momoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.23,0:21:50.12,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.74,0:21:52.19,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.03,0:21:57.48,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what I would've done if you didn't answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.33,0:22:03.97,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.24,0:22:16.33,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.44,0:22:20.63,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you too, Momoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.35,0:22:57.16,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.16,0:22:58.84,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I want it shorter.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.84,0:22:59.73,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.03,0:23:28.23,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Momoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.94,0:23:30.36,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.36,0:23:32.71,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you. I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.37,0:23:54.81,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs50\fad(0,2000)\fnFlorence\b1\pos(340,272)}Even if my body turns to ash,{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.37,0:23:54.81,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs50\fad(0,2000)\fnFlorence\b1\pos(337,414)}I will never leave your side.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.74,0:24:07.65,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, Lady Shinobu didn't come back that night.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.44,0:24:11.67,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I can help!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.35,0:24:13.89,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.89,0:24:16.01,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,But this is Momoko's, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.21,0:24:19.05,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,...I want to carry it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.87,0:24:24.87,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Before long, Kirin moved into Matsuri's room,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.61,0:24:30.87,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,and Lady Shinobu and I took over the attic.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.87,0:24:35.78,Signs,,0000,0030,0320,,{\fad(0,0)}{\pos(320,75)}{\p1}{\bord0.5\shad0}m 0 0 l 165 0 165 50 0 50{\p0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.87,0:24:35.78,Signs - Text,,0000,0030,0320,,{\fs30\pos(320,70)}Poetry Room
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.63,0:24:35.78,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,The three of us left the poetry club.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.97,0:24:47.17,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,It's cold, but it feels good, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.76,0:24:50.56,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,This will be my sanctuary from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.08,0:24:54.59,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Miss Naito okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.33,0:24:58.16,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I'll go see her after we graduate.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.15,0:25:05.27,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if my body turns to ash...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.92,0:25:12.54,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,...I will never leave your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.13,0:25:21.47,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Shinobu?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.71,0:25:27.05,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll love whoever you love too!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.81,0:25:29.18,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Maya...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.60,0:25:39.56,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I could taste tears in that kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.78,0:25:44.14,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What will come after this pain?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.14,0:25:45.83,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't know.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.89,0:25:51.69,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But this will be my eternal first love.{\i0}
